# Minimal Hello World

show "Hello, World!"

# Variables
name is "Jules"
age is 7

# Show variables
show "My name is " + name
show "I am " + age + " years old"

# Simple conditional
when age is 7 then
    show "I am seven years old!"
otherwise
    show "I am not seven years old!"
done

# Simple loop
show "Counting from 1 to 5:"
i is 1
while i less than or equal to 5
    show i
    i is i + 1
done 